  • public class NonRebroadcastingKnowledgeDataManager
extends KnowledgeDataManager
    cz.cuni.mff.d3s.deeco.network.KnowledgeDataManager without rebroadcasting feature. Otherwise it's almost the same implementation as cz.cuni.mff.d3s.deeco.network.DefaultKnowledgeDataManager --------------------------- Created by Jakub Kinst 2014 E-mail: jakub@kinst.cz
